.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, martial-arts, superhero
House: townhouse, futuristic, tower, colonial, cottage
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, rowing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is the futuristic house##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 3. the colonial house is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 7. the cottage house is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the tower house is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the cottage house##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person watching superhero movies and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | collecting | singing     | puzzles   | filmmaking   | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | documentary | adventure | martial-arts | family        |
