.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, siglo, havana, oliveros, chaman
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, hip-hop, house, trance
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the oliveros-smoker is between the person watching crime movies and the havana-smoker##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the oliveros-smoker##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the chaman-smoker and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the havana-smoker is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Cigar           | siglo | havana | oliveros | chaman    | bolivar  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | blues        | ambient   | house    | trance     |

